{"TopicId":132474,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Enhanced Mirror Symmetry","CreatedByName":"TheGreatB3","CreatedById":146335,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-19T14:00:33Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"TheGreatB3","CreatedById":146335,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-19T14:00:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe game currently supports 1-way mirror symmetry. \u00A0I would like to see support added for 2-way and possibly 4-way mirror symmetry. \u00A0I feel like this would greatly simplify\u00A0building of both spaceplanes and rockets. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe class=\u0022imgur-album\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022550\u0022 src=\u0022//imgur.com/a/1slMS/embed?background=ffffff\u0026amp;text=1a1a1a\u0026amp;link=4e76c9\u0022 width=\u0022100%\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-19T19:47:44Z\u0022 title=\u002202/19/2016 07:47  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 19, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by TheGreatB3\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eadded Imgur album\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-19T18:33:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not sure what you mean by \u0022x-way\u0022 mirror symmetry.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould you provide an illustrative image?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-19T18:39:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou already have up to 8x symmetry available. What are you asking for?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheGreatB3","CreatedById":146335,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-19T18:48:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222419077\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132474\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455906797\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258517\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022spink00\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, spink00 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not sure what you mean by \u0022x-way\u0022 mirror symmetry.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould you provide an illustrative image?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was trying to, but I\u0027m not sure how to embed an Imgur album.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-19T18:49:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222419106\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132474\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455907688\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146335\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheGreatB3\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, TheGreatB3 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nembed an Imgur album.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is an imgur button on the far right of the editor.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheGreatB3","CreatedById":146335,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-19T19:00:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222419109\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132474\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455907763\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258517\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022spink00\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, spink00 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is an imgur button on the far right of the editor.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWouldn\u0027t work for me. \u00A0Here\u0027s the link:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/a/1slMS\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://imgur.com/a/1slMS\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-19T19:19:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like that idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBy the by, using your album\u0027s ID as an example, in imgur.com/a/1slMS, you would only paste the \u00221slMS\u0022 into the imgur button.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe class=\u0022imgur-album\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022550\u0022 src=\u0022//imgur.com/a/1slMS/embed?background=ffffff\u0026amp;text=1a1a1a\u0026amp;link=4e76c9\u0022 width=\u0022100%\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-19T19:40:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI get this (I think).\u00A0 Radial symmetry rotates copies of the original around the \u0027core\u0027, while what the OP suggests would flip their orientation too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s easier to see with deployed landing gear. \u00A0With radial symmetry the wheels all point\u00A0around the core in the same, clockwise or anticlockwise,\u00A0direction that the original points in.\u00A0 What the OP suggests is multiple mirror \u0027planes\u0027 rather than just the one mirror we currently have, so with the same landing gear mirrored twice you would get 3\u00A0copies of it, one pointing the same way as\u00A0the original and two more pointing the opposite way.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNeat idea, I could see it coming in handy actually.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AbacusWizard","CreatedById":116476,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-19T22:38:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat would make rover and aircraft design much easier!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Atlas2342","CreatedById":155194,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-20T04:19:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis would make building SLS side boosters easier....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}